Pre-Game Insights: Heinrich Malan, Ireland Men's Head Coach, emphasized that Ireland will not be treating their seven games as warmups, and they will aim to win as many of those games as possible.
The T20 format is fast-paced, think-on-your-feet style of cricket, and finding a way to win is a skill that can only be learned and developed on the field of play.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Ireland Men are presently ranked 11th in the world in T20Is, aiming to make an impact in the upcoming series and tournaments.
The squads for the Pakistan T20I series, Tri-Series in Netherlands, and T20 World Cup in US/Caribbean are announced.
